-> Installing prisma
  npm i -D prisma@latest
  npm i @prisma/client

-> Initializing prisma
  npx prisma init

-> Work on schema.prisma to add/delete/alter models
-> To create migration
  npx prisma migrate dev --create-only

-> To push the migrations to db
  npx prisma db push
  
-> To visualize prisma table
  npx prisma studio
